OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fmostly dry with clear spells through
OL,7,Fthe evening and overnight, but the odd
OL,8,Fshower possible around the north
OL,9,Fcoast. Breezy at times in the evening,
OL,10,Feasing overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FLargely dry with bright or
OL,13,Fsunny spells, but chance of the odd
OL,14,Fshower. A bit cooler than recent days.
OL,15,FChance of rain in the southeast in the
OL,16,Fafternoon and evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
