OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FChance
OL,6,Fof cloud and rain in southeast at
OL,7,Ffirst Saturday, otherwise dry and
OL,8,Fbright. Cloudy and windy at times with
OL,9,Foccasional spells of rain on Sunday
OL,10,Fand Monday.
